{"tid":1238560,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我發左個夢，我地搞到中國有民主。","createTime":"2019-06-18T00:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T02:23:30.000Z","uid":203413,"like":8,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a584b94cec2dffd7cefa92349f321f192215a2dc","tid":1238560,"uid":203413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:59:01.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我發左個夢，五十年不變之後，可能我地比中國法治搞到退步哂。<br />\n<br />\n其實中國內地唔係無心水清既人。只不過大多數人無足夠資訊去了解。而我地現有既優勢就係支那打壓唔到我地。點解唔諗啲計仔去幫支那打通打通任督二脈，令佢地覺醒呢？<br />\n<br />\n要一個支那進步，好過比一個香港消失仲好啦。<br />\n<br />\n真係發夢見到。會唔會係我太天真先夢見到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f30845915e564d92fbc81333a4f6645ae6dd2f1","tid":1238560,"uid":42268,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:00:11.000Z","msg":"你仲未醒"},{"pid":"076bee3ee0e4ca6297e2cd177020b24c1d049d0d","tid":1238560,"uid":29093,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你太耐無打 j,  發埋啲自high. 春夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b39d838a9478a31c5adee59f24275130d72eaf0","tid":1238560,"uid":203413,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"6f30845915e564d92fbc81333a4f6645ae6dd2f1","tid":1238560,"uid":42268,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:00:11.000Z","msg":"你仲未醒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:01:08.000Z","msg":"我諗係啦"},{"pid":"c01e4f8de758ba8e2d615077aafc7a26574b4034","tid":1238560,"uid":127561,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:01:17.000Z","msg":"叫中共改好簡直與虎謀皮"},{"pid":"ef19ba90278a9fa281ea3c5ea93508253a8925dc","tid":1238560,"uid":9128,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01: